<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="arrival-n">arrival <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'raɪvl/    美 /ə'raɪvl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-c">1.★ <strong>[U] &amp; [C] 到来；到达：</strong></h4>
<p>反 departure </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the arrivals lounge
抵达大厅</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We hope for the arrival of good news. 
我们盼望着好消息的到来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>On</strong> / <strong>Upon arrival</strong>, Jimmy found a long line of applicants waiting to be interviewed.  
一到那里，吉米就发现申请者排起了长队等着面试。</p><footer>2013 山东</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 到达者；到达物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>early / late / new arrivals
早到/晚到/新到者</p></div></div>